sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant GoalDetail
    participant MilestoneSteps
    participant Validation
    participant Store
    participant APIService
    participant Backend
    participant Database
    
    User->>GoalDetail: Navigate to milestone goal detail page
    GoalDetail->>MilestoneSteps: Display milestones using Ant Design Steps
    MilestoneSteps->>User: Show all milestones with status: pending
    
    User->>MilestoneSteps: Click "Mark Complete" on Milestone 1
    MilestoneSteps->>Validation: Validate: No dependencies (first milestone)
    Validation-->>MilestoneSteps: Validation passed
    
    MilestoneSteps->>Store: Optimistic update: completeMilestonePending()
    Store->>Store: Update milestone status in store
    Store->>Store: Recalculate progress optimistically
    
    MilestoneSteps->>APIService: completeMilestone(goalId, milestoneId)
    APIService->>Backend: PATCH /api/goals/:id/milestones/:milestoneId
    
    Backend->>Database: Load goal from database
    Database-->>Backend: Goal with milestones
    
    Backend->>Backend: Find milestone by ID
    Backend->>Validation: Validate dependencies server-side
    Validation-->>Backend: All dependencies met
    
    Backend->>Backend: Validate sequential completion (if required)
    Backend->>Backend: Update milestone: status = 'completed', completedDate = now
    Backend->>Backend: Recalculate overall progress: (1/5) * 100 = 20%
    
    Backend->>Backend: Check: All milestones completed?
    Backend->>Backend: No, continue
    
    Backend->>Database: UPDATE goal SET progress=?, milestones=?, updatedAt=?
    Database-->>Backend: Updated goal
    
    Backend-->>APIService: 200 OK with updated goal
    APIService->>Store: completeMilestoneSuccess(goal)
    Store->>Store: Replace optimistic update
    Store->>Store: Update goal in store
    Store->>Store: Update milestone status
    
    MilestoneSteps->>User: Update Steps component: Milestone 1 shows as completed
    MilestoneSteps->>User: Update progress bar: 20%
    MilestoneSteps->>User: Next milestone (2) enabled
    
    Note over User,Database: User continues completing milestones 2, 3, 4...
    
    User->>MilestoneSteps: Click "Mark Complete" on Milestone 5 (last)
    MilestoneSteps->>Validation: Validate dependencies
    Validation-->>MilestoneSteps: All dependencies met
    
    MilestoneSteps->>APIService: completeMilestone(goalId, milestoneId5)
    APIService->>Backend: PATCH /api/goals/:id/milestones/:milestoneId5
    Backend->>Backend: Update milestone 5
    Backend->>Backend: Recalculate progress: (5/5) * 100 = 100%
    Backend->>Backend: Check: All milestones completed? YES
    Backend->>Backend: Suggest completion
    
    Backend-->>APIService: 200 OK with goal (progress: 100%)
    APIService->>Store: completeMilestoneSuccess(goal)
    Store->>Store: Update goal
    
    MilestoneSteps->>User: Show: "All milestones completed! Mark goal as complete?"
    User->>MilestoneSteps: Confirm completion
    MilestoneSteps->>APIService: Complete goal
    APIService->>Backend: Update goal status to 'completed'
    Backend->>Database: UPDATE goal SET status='completed', completedDate=now
    Database-->>Backend: Goal completed
    
    GoalDetail->>User: Show goal as completed

